data.description: 2.73 acres completely fenced, cleared AND in an X flood zone (no flood insurance required). High and dry 4 bedroom 2 bath home.  Cooks kitchen and vaulted ceilings.  Strong concrete block home with stucco and hurricane shutters.  Off Everglades Blvd and Golden Gate Blvd- close to shops. If the 75 and Everglades Blvd exit EVER opens, you'll be glad you live HERE! Vanderbilt Beach Road will be extended to 18th st NE soon. Golden Gate Estates is THE place to live if you love to have all your toys in your yard with NO HOA! There are 2 concrete pads and permits ready for a 20'X60' workshop to store boats, 4 wheelers, kayaks, RV's, etc. You can have 2 horses here. BRAND new a/c system. New flooring and kitchen. VERY quiet here with absolutely no road noise. 2005 built home that has been lovingly redone
